msgid ""
"The common approach for such use cases is to create a 'link' module. In our case, the module "
"would depend on ``estate`` and ``account`` and would include the invoice creation logic of the "
"estate property. This way the real estate and the accounting modules can be installed "
"independently. When both are installed, the link module provides the new feature."
msgstr ""
