#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:324
msgid "`Owl: Reactivity <https://github.com/odoo/owl/blob/master/doc/v2/reference/reactivity.md>`_"
