#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:470
msgid "12. Deleting todos"
msgstr "၁၂။ Todo များ ဖျက်ခြင်း"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:472
