msgid "Insert :code:`<span class=\"fa fa-remove\"/>` in the template of the `TodoItem` component."
msgstr "`TodoItem` component ၏ template ထဲတွင် :code:`<span class=\"fa fa-remove\"/>` ကို ထည့်ပါ။"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:476
msgid "Whenever the user clicks on it, it should call the `removeTodo` method."
msgstr "User က ၎င်းကို နှိပ်တိုင်း `removeTodo` method ကို ခေါ်သင့်သည်။"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/discover_js_framework/01_owl_components.rst:480
msgid ""
"If you're using an array to store your todo list, you can use the JavaScript `splice` function to"
