"များထဲတွင် ထိုအတိုင်း define လုပ်နိုင်သည်။"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:205
msgid "You can set various attributes for your new field. For basic fields, these include:"
msgstr "Field အသစ်အတွက် attribute အမျိုးမျိုး သတ်မှတ်နိုင်သည်။ Basic field များအတွက် အောက်ပါတို့ ပါဝင်သည်။"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:207
msgid "`name`: the technical name of the field (must begin with `x_`)"
msgstr "`name`: field ၏ technical name (`x_` ဖြင့် စရမည်)"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:208
msgid "`field_description`: the label of the field"
msgstr "`field_description`: field ၏ label"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:209
msgid "`help`: a help text for the field, displayed in the interface"
msgstr "`help`: interface တွင် ပြသမည့် field အတွက် help text"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:210
msgid "`ttype`: the type of the field (e.g. `char`, `integer`, `float`, `html`, etc.)"
msgstr "`ttype`: field ၏ type (ဥပမာ `char`, `integer`, `float`, `html` စသည်)"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:211
msgid "`required`: whether the field is required or not (default: `False`)"
msgstr "`required`: field သည် required ဖြစ်မဖြစ် (default: `False`)"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:212
msgid "`readonly`: whether the field is read-only or not (default: `False`)"
msgstr "`readonly`: field သည် read-only ဖြစ်မဖြစ် (default: `False`)"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:213
msgid "`index`: whether the field is indexed or not (default: `False`)"
msgstr "`index`: field သည် indexed ဖြစ်မဖြစ် (default: `False`)"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:214
msgid ""
"`copied`: whether the field is copied when duplicating a record or not (default: `True` for non-"
"relational non-computed fields, `False` for relational and computed fields)"
msgstr ""
"`copied`: record duplicate လုပ်သောအခါ field ကို copy လုပ်မလုပ် (non-relational non-computed field"
" များအတွက် default: `True`; relational နှင့် computed field များအတွက် `False`)"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/tutorials/importable_modules.rst:216
msgid "`translate`: whether the field is translatable or not (default: `False`)"
msgstr "`translate`: field သည် translatable ဖြစ်မဖြစ် (default: `False`)"

