#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/howtos/create_reports.rst:71
msgid ""
"`tools.drop_view_if_exists` ensures that a conflicting view is not created when the SQL query is "
"executed. It is standard to separate the different parts of the query to allow for easier model "
"extension. Exactly how the query is split up across methods is not standardized, but at minimum, "
"the `_select` and `_from` methods are common, and of course, all these methods will return "
"strings."
msgstr ""
"`tools.drop_view_if_ ရှိနေတယ်။` ensures that a conflicting view is not created when the SQL query"
" is executed. It is standard to separate the different parts of the query to allow for easier "
"model extension. Exactly how the query is split up across methods is not standardized, but at "
"minimum, the `_ရွေးချယ်ပါ။` and `_from` နည်းလမ်းများသည် သာမာန်ဖြစ်ပြီး၊ ဤနည်းလမ်းအားလုံးသည် "
"စာကြောင်းများကို ပြန်ပေးပါမည်။"

