msgstr "`position-relative` ကို ဥပမာအဖြစ် ယူပါ။"

#: ../../home/slo/Documents/Projects/odoo19_docs/content/developer/howtos/scss_tips.rst:186
msgid ""
"Since a utility-class is defined, any CSS line with the declaration `position: relative` is "
